OL,7,FYouth unemployment is on the rise -
OL,8,Fand young people from working-class
OL,9,Fbackgrounds in Wales are now the least
OL,10,Flikely to have a job in the UK.
OL,12,FSouth East Wales has seen the biggest
OL,13,Fdrop in employment this year, with
OL,14,FRhondda Cynon Taf recording the lowest
OL,15,Fnumber of young people in work across
OL,16,Fthe region.
OL,18,FOne of those who is searching for work
OL,19,Fin the Rhondda Valley is 18-year-old
OL,20,FSophie Thompson from Llwynypia.
