OL,4,Cfears she'll be on universal credit
OL,5,Cfor life
OL,7,F"Opportunities in the Rhondda are
OL,8,Fawful, there just aren't enough of
OL,9,Fthem," Sophie told S4C's current
OL,10,Faffairs programme, Y Byd ar Bedwar.
OL,12,FOnly 44.9% of 16 to 24-year-olds in
OL,13,FRhondda Cynon Taf are in employment,
OL,14,Fbelow the Welsh average of 52.5%.
OL,16,FWithin her first month of being
OL,17,Funemployed, Sophie says she applied
OL,18,Ffor nearly 50 jobs, but with no luck.
