OL,3,C18 year old from the Rhondda valley
OL,4,Cfears she'll be on universal credit
OL,5,Cfor life
OL,7,F"When I hear back from employers, they
OL,8,Fusually say 'you haven't got enough
OL,9,Fexperience', but most of the time it's
OL,10,Fradio silence, I don't hear anything
OL,11,Fback," Sophie said.
OL,13,F"I just want someone to see I'm trying
OL,14,Fso hard."
OL,16,F"I want them to say 'she's got the
OL,17,F(GCSE) grades, the motivation to do
OL,18,Fit, I want her to do the job.'"
OL,20,F'The Government should do more'
