OL,5,Cfor life
OL,7,FFollowing a number of rejections,
OL,8,FSophie turned to her local JobCentre
OL,9,Ffor support and began to receive
OL,10,FUniversal Credit - a benefit for
OL,11,Fpeople who are unemployed or on a low
OL,12,Fincome. Sophie now receives around
OL,13,F#311 a month, and to qualify for this,
OL,14,Fshe has to prove that she's spent 35
OL,15,Fhours a week looking for a job.
OL,17,FIn September this year, the number of
OL,18,Fpeople claiming universal credit
OL,19,Fincreased to 418,000, a record high.
