OL,7,F"I want to do something with my
OL,8,Flife... I just need someone to give me
OL,9,Fa chance."
OL,11,FIn a statement, the Welsh Government
OL,12,Fsays, "We understand the challenges
OL,13,Ffaced by many young people in securing
OL,14,Fwork, which is why we put in place the
OL,15,FYoung Person's Guarantee, helping 16-
OL,16,F24 year olds in Wales secure a place
OL,17,Fin education, training, find a job or
OL,18,Feven start their own business. We want
OL,19,Fyoung people to thrive in our Welsh
OL,20,Feconomy.
