OL,7,F"Since its launch, the Young Person's
OL,8,FGuarantee has helped over 60,000 young
OL,9,Fpeople take part in employability and
OL,10,Fskills programmes in Wales. Of those,
OL,11,Falmost 9,000 young people have
OL,12,Fprogressed into employment, and more
OL,13,Fthan 850 have started their own
OL,14,Fbusiness."
